When generating a Git commit message, follow this format exactly:

Type: Subject

Allowed types: Feature, CI, New, Tweak, Fix, Experiment, Deprecate, Deprecated, Revert, Internal
Subject must start with an uppercase letter (sentence-case).
Header must be at most 100 characters.
Do not include a body or footer.
Do not end the subject with a period.

Examples:
- Feature: Add playlist download support
- Fix: Resolve crash when URL field is empty
- Tweak: Improve progress bar responsiveness
- CI: Add commit message linting workflow
- Internal: Refactor download manager threading
